title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Sumo (Remix)
content: Smash your way through foes in Sumo (Remix) and battle it out to hold your spot in a shrinking and moving safe zone on a platform above the sky. Survive until the timer runs out or risk spontaneous combustion for 2X GTA$ and RP through June 19.
